... The Numogram vindicates The Chaldean Geometry, 90 + 81 + 72 + 63 + 54 = 360. It divides into inner and outer regions, 81 + 72 + 54 = 207, and 90 + 63 = 153, respectively. Xenotic Cosmogony is thus primarily partitioned by these two numbers. ...
... 207, the number of the cosmos (the Hexad of the Yijing for example), is strictly localized within The Numogram as the non-whole. ...

... Consilience is the project of integrating all knowledge,  from physics to the arts and religion, within a common ('consilient') framework of understanding. The number of Consilience is 207 (AQ). Quod erat demonstrandum.
